[(Private Generic IO)]

Detailed Description

Struct to hold info about the file format for subset.

Description:

Holds information pertinent to file IO for a subset.

NOTE: purposefully do not have any dynamically allocated bits in here or we have to have a special free call (see _FC_DsFileIOInfo).
